(31, 'com_content.article', '10th house in horoscope', 'karma-bhava', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;10th house is popularly known as Karma Bhava in Vedic Astrology. <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=1:surya&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Surya</a> is the karaka for 10th house but in some text <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=7:shani&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Shani</a> is considered the karaka for karma bhava. It is the house which defines your career and public reputation. Most important of all it defines your purpose in life which when attained can satisfy your birth as a &nbsp;human. Every human being is sent with a specific purpose which would make a difference in the lives to those around him.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Some people are born to be Politicians while others are born to be Sweepers. The only difference is Politicians dirties the system while the Sweeper cleans it. So who is more important of the two? You can take a good guess as to who would be approved by people and the maker aka God. While the career of a person maybe defined by past life karma the actions in this life define his reputation and future karma. There is nothing to be worried about a job post or public standing. Instead focusing on doing the job with hard work and diligence is the right way to go about life. Regretfully myself included most people worry about their line of work and position more then the quality of work, satisfaction that comes with it and the output delivered to the society.&nbsp;10th house is also called Pitru Bhava or Father''s House. Father''s character and personality as well as relationship with child can be known through 10th house. Devil-in-disguise known as the Boss as well as familiar foe called Mother-in-Law are also governed by the 10h house.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;10th house deals with leadership qualities, administration, father and political ambitions. While exact type of profession is better defined through a range of permutation and combinations atleast a rough sketch can be provided by 10th house for people looking at a career choice. Surya in 10th house can give a career in agriculture especially production of food grains but also give career in Politics and Administration. <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=2:chandra&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Chandra</a> is good for cultivation of fruits and vegetables as a profession but also good with business of watery goods as well as business on foreign shores. For <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=3:mangal&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Mangal</a> career in defense sector and medical surgery is a possible option. <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=4:buddh&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Budh</a> can make a good businessman, career in teaching, accounting and software services. <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=5:guru&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Guru</a> in 10th house can be good for work in charitable trusts, religious places and fund-raisers. Please note that exact profession seems to vastly differ in case of Guru. <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=6:shukra&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Shukra</a> in 10th house can make a fortune out of selling beauty products, cosmetics, fashion industry as well as design and jewelry. Shani while gives a good profession in hardware, Oil Import-Export as well as Politics, one needs a mention of the pitfalls of Shani in 10th house. Shani has the habit of elevating person to the top of success ladder but afterwards throwing him face first on the ground when he occupies the 10th house. <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=8:rahu&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Rahu</a> can make up a good Politician or Actor if other placements are favorable. Bottom line with Rahu is person puts up a mask. <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=9:ketu&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Ketu</a> amounts for a topsy-turvy career though exact range of profession differs like in case of Guru. A person attains success after considerable efforts when Ketu occupies the 10th house.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;10th house is the house of obligation and duties. Irrespective of the profession there would be few living souls who look forward to performing their duties and maintaining a decorum befitting of their post. Everyone likes to neglect their duties and take undue advantage of the power that comes with the post. If not all the time it maybe true on some instances. The seeds of success or failure are sown in the 10th house. It is the house where your thoughts and actions make or break your reputation. Choose carefully the path you must take and choose wisely is the profound advice to the readers.&nbsp;</p>', 1, '', 0, 1, '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 0, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 899, '', '2014-02-01 12:20:34', 899, '2014-02-03 13:25:29', '*', '2014-02-01 12:20:34', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 19, 117, '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', 0, 2, 2, '', '', 11, '', 1),
(32, 'com_content.article', '11th house in horoscope', 'labh-bhava', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;11th house is known as Labh Bhava in Vedic Astrology. Also known as House of Gains, 11th house looks after friendship, elder brothers, networks at market place, social progress, oppurtunities for economic growth, gains and profits from market place. The karaka for 11th house is <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=5:guru&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Guru</a>. Labh Bhava determines income for an individual. If the 11th house and lord of 11th house are in good condition then income of an individual remains healthy. The reverse is true if 11th house and its lord are in bad condition. 11th house also manages the quantity and quality of friends.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;There can be no savings as long as there is not a steady flow of income. It wouldn''t be an overstatement to say that atleast savings department of the <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=11:dhana-bhava&amp;catid=10:12-houses&amp;Itemid=110">2nd house</a> is subservient to the income department of the 11th house. In modern world where Money has gained so much prominense it has led to a scenario where the 11th house dictates terms on many matters of other houses particularly 2nd house, <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=14:putra-bhava&amp;catid=10:12-houses&amp;Itemid=110">5th house</a> and <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=16:kalatra-bhava&amp;catid=10:12-houses&amp;Itemid=110">7th house</a>. No Money means No Savings. No Savings means No Marriage. No Marriage means no Social Identity. While this does not necessarily apply to every individual it holds true for many poor souls. Relationship of 11th house with other house lords could signal income through multiple portfolio''s. The better the condition of 11th house and 11th house lord the more beneficial results are obtained in matters of friends, income, social and business connections as well as chances for growth. Reverse is the case when 11th house and its lord are in problematic condition. While affiliation with the hell houses is not the most ideal scenario it may yield favorable results in the lords of hell house and lord of 11th house are friendly planets.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Labh Bhava also determines your friends and social circle. Imagine no friends on facebook or no connection on google plus or no followers on twitter. No real friends at school, work place or in general life. 11th house along with <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=12:sahaja-bhava&amp;catid=10:12-houses&amp;Itemid=110">3rd house</a> has gained prominence in the last few decades. Today 11th house is much more then means of livelihood and income. It controls your social standing through friends and professional standing through network connections. From a business perspective 11th house is the house of networks at market place. Any thriving business needs to be in contact with influential people at the market place. A good condition of 11th house ensures a businessman is always connected with the right people at the right position at the right time.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Most planets give favorable results in the 11th house baring <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=6:shukra&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Shukra</a>. <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=5:guru&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Guru</a> as the karaka for 11th house is the most ideal planet to have in the 11th house. It increases income, friends and social prestige and also improves networks and business connections. <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=4:buddh&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Budh</a> gives highly communicative, well-connected friends and friends who have a good intellect. <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=7:shani&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Shani</a> in 11th house makes a dedicated worker who improves wealth through sincere hard work. Shukra though bad in 11th house can provide income through arts, fashion and music. <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=8:rahu&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Rahu</a> gives material yearnings and increases association with a wide variety of people.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;11th house is the house which makes or breaks an individual through financial and social means. While it doesn''t have much bearing on the individual as a whole for those who put too much emphasis on money and power it is essential that they have a good 11th house.&nbsp;</p>', 1, '', 0, 1, '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 0, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 899, '', '2014-02-01 12:21:25', 899, '2014-02-03 13:25:48', '*', '2014-02-01 12:21:25', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 20, 119, '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', 0, 2, 1, '', '', 11, '', 1),
(33, 'com_content.article', '12th house in horoscope', 'vyaya-bhava', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;12th house is popularly known as Vyaya Bhava in Vedic Astrology. It is the house which gives grief, despair and losses to an individual. Losses are not just monetary but also emotional and physical. As one of the hell houses it can literally put individuals through the motions and create depression and anxities of unparallel quantities. 12th house also rules over prisons, ashrams, hospitals and mental institutions. On a better note it also rules research and doctarate programmes. But the most important of all is that the 12th house provides Moksha to an individual.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;No one likes matters of the 12th house. Who would want to voluntarily go to prisons, hospitals or mental institutions? Who would like depression grief, despair and losses? Impact of 12th house is huge and the tag of Valley of Despair is apt for matters of this house. But after careful observation and practical experience a hypothesis starts to develop that the 12th house is perhaps the most misunderstood house in astrology.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;While not many people reading this article would care to get Moksha, it is essential to know that no rebirth equates to no suffering. For those who do not believe in the concept of Moksha, there is higher knowledge and deeper meaning of life associated with the 12th house. An individual gains an understanding of concepts which are outside the scope of what is already known. This is the reason why research and doctarate programmes are under the wings of the 12th house as these are fields where knowledge is not yet present in this world. For those who don''t care two hoots about Moksha or Knowldge there is the most important aspect called bed pleasures ruled by 12th house. Many marriages break on complaints of incomplete or no sexual satisfaction derived from partners. 12th house ascertains whether you have a good life in bed or not. Perhaps more importantly it guarantees that your marriage is not broken on account of non-existent physical relationship with your partner.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;12th house on the positive side also rules dreams and imagination. All the successful fictional writers are blessed with distinctive and vivid imagination by blessings of the 12th house. Not only that lecturers and researchers, Ashrams and Hospitals run by blessings of the 12th house. 12th house has lots of negatives but equal amount of positives. It all comes down to perspective in the end.&nbsp;</p>', 1, '', 0, 1, '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 0, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 899, '', '2014-02-01 12:22:38', 899, '2014-02-03 13:26:22', '*', '2014-02-01 12:22:38', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 21, 121, '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', 0, 2, 0, '', '', 11, '', 1),
(34, 'com_content.article', 'Mesha', 'aries', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Aries is known as Mesha in Vedic Astrology. This fiery sign is a male by gender and rules the east direction. It gives Pitta Dosha. It controls the head, face and brain. <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=3:mangal&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Mangal</a> is the lord of mesha rashi. <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=1:surya&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Surya</a> is exalted in mesha while <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=7:shani&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Shani</a> is debilitated in mesha rashi.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>', 1, '', 0, 1, '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 0, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 899, '', '2014-02-01 12:23:46', 899, '2014-02-03 13:26:51', '*', '2014-02-01 12:23:46', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 22, 123, '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', 0, 2, 10, '', '', 12, '', 1),
(35, 'com_content.article', 'Vrishabha', 'taurus', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Taurus is known as Vrishabha Rashi in Vedic Astrology. It is an earthy sign. By gender it is a female and rules the south direction. It controls the mouth, neck and voice box. It gives both Vata and Kapha Dosha. <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=6:shukra&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Shukra</a> is the lord of Vrishabha Rashi while <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=2:chandra&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Chandra</a> is exalted in Vrishabha Rashi.&nbsp;</p>', 1, '', 0, 1, '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 0, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 899, '', '2014-02-01 12:24:41', 899, '2014-02-03 13:27:12', '*', '2014-02-01 12:24:41', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 23, 125, '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', 0, 2, 9, '', '', 12, '', 1),
(36, 'com_content.article', 'Mithuna', 'gemini', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Gemini is known as Mithuna in Vedic Astrology. This windy sign is male by gender and rules the west direction. It gives Vatta Dosha. It rules the chest, hands and rib cage. <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=4:buddh&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Budh</a> is the lord of Mithuna.</p>', 1, '', 0, 1, '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 0, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 899, '', '2014-02-01 12:25:34', 899, '2014-02-03 13:27:30', '*', '2014-02-01 12:25:34', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 24, 127, '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', 0, 2, 8, '', '', 12, '', 1),
(37, 'com_content.article', 'Karka', 'cancer', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Cancer is known as Karka Rashi in Vedic Astrology. It is a watery sign and female by gender. It rules the north direction. It gives Kapah dosha. It controls the chest, lungs and heart. <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=2:chandra&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Chandra</a> is the lord of Karka. <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=5:guru&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Guru</a> is exalted in Karka while <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=3:mangal&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Mangal</a> is debilitated in Karka.&nbsp;</p>', 1, '', 0, 1, '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 0, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 899, '', '2014-02-01 12:26:19', 899, '2014-02-03 13:27:52', '*', '2014-02-01 12:26:19', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 25, 129, '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', 0, 2, 7, '', '', 12, '', 1),
(38, 'com_content.article', 'Simha', 'leo', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Leo is called Simha Rashi in Vedic Astrology. &nbsp;The naturally fiery sign rules the east direction and is a male by gender. It gives Pitta Dosha. It controls the stomach, spinal cord and back. <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=1:surya&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Surya</a> is the lord of Simha Rashi.&nbsp;</p>', 1, '', 0, 1, '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 0, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 899, '', '2014-02-01 12:27:43', 899, '2014-02-03 13:28:22', '*', '2014-02-01 12:27:43', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 26, 131, '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', 0, 2, 6, '', '', 12, '', 1),
(39, 'com_content.article', 'Kanya', 'virgo', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Virgo is known as Kanya Rashi in Vedic Astrology. It is an earthy sign, female by gender and rules the south direction. It give both Vata Dosha and Kapha Dosha. <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=4:buddh&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Budh</a> is the lord of Kanya Rashi. Budh is exalted and <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=6:shukra&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Shukra</a> is debilitated in Kanya Rashi.&nbsp;</p>', 1, '', 0, 1, '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 0, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 899, '', '2014-02-01 12:30:47', 899, '2014-02-03 13:28:51', '*', '2014-02-01 12:30:47', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 27, 133, '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', 0, 2, 5, '', '', 12, '', 1),
(40, 'com_content.article', 'Tula', 'libra', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; Libra is known as Tula Rashi in Vedic Astrology. The windy sign rules the west direction and is a male by gender. It controls the kidneys and urinary system as well as sexual organs. It gives Vatta Dosha. <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=6:shukra&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Shukra</a> is the lord of Tula Rashi. <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=7:shani&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Shani</a> is exalted and <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=1:surya&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Surya</a> is debilitated in Tula Rashi.&nbsp;</p>', 1, '', 0, 1, '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 0, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 899, '', '2014-02-01 12:34:24', 899, '2014-02-03 13:30:57', '*', '2014-02-01 12:34:24', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 28, 135, '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', 0, 4, 4, '', '', 12, '', 1),
(41, 'com_content.article', 'Vrischika', 'scorpio', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Scorpio is known as Vrischika Rashi in Vedic Astrology. This watery sign is a female by gender and rules over the north direction. It controls the uterus, bladder and excretary system. <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=3:mangal&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Mangal</a> is the lord of Vrischika Rashi while <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=2:chandra&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Chandra</a> is debilitated in Vrischika Rashi.&nbsp;</p>', 1, '', 0, 1, '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 0, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 899, '', '2014-02-01 12:36:13', 899, '2014-02-03 13:30:06', '*', '2014-02-01 12:36:13', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 29, 137, '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', 0, 2, 3, '', '', 12, '', 1),
(42, 'com_content.article', 'Dhana', 'sagittarius', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Saggitarius is popularly known as Dhana Rashi (not to be confused with <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=11:dhana-bhava&amp;catid=10:12-houses&amp;Itemid=110">dhana bhava</a>) in Vedic Astrology. Dhana Rashi is a fiery sign, by gender a male and rules the east direction. It causes Pitta Dosha. It controls the thighs. <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=5:guru&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Guru</a> is the lord of Dhana Rashi and <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=8:rahu&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Rahu</a> is said to be neecha in Dhana Rashi.&nbsp;</p>', 1, '', 0, 1, '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 0, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 899, '', '2014-02-01 12:43:34', 899, '2014-02-03 13:30:47', '*', '2014-02-01 12:43:34', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 30, 139, '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', 0, 3, 1, '', '', 12, '', 1),
(43, 'com_content.article', 'Makara', 'capricorn', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Capricorn is popularly known as Makara in Vedic Astrology. This earthy sign is female by gender and rules the south direction. It gives both Vatta and Pitta Dosha. It controls both the knee joints and parts around it. <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=7:shani&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Shani</a> is the lord of Makara Rashi. <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=3:mangal&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Mangal</a> is exalted and <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=5:guru&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Guru</a> is debilitated in makara.</p>', 1, '', 0, 1, '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 0, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 899, '', '2014-02-01 12:44:07', 899, '2014-02-03 13:31:26', '*', '2014-02-01 12:44:07', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 31, 141, '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', 0, 2, 2, '', '', 12, '', 1),
(44, 'com_content.article', 'Kumbha', 'aquarius', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Aquarius is known as Kumbha in Vedic Astrology. This windy sign has a male gender and rules the west direction . It gives Vayu Dosha. It rules the feet especially the parts below knee joints. <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=7:shani&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Shani</a> is the lord of Kumbha rashi while <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=8:rahu&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Rahu</a> is said to be exalted in Kumbha.&nbsp;</p>', 1, '', 0, 1, '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 0, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 899, '', '2014-02-01 12:45:20', 899, '2014-02-03 13:31:46', '*', '2014-02-01 12:45:20', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 32, 143, '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', 0, 2, 1, '', '', 12, '', 1),
(45, 'com_content.article', 'Meena', 'pisces', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Pisces is known as Meena Rashi in Vedic Astrology. It is a watery sign, female by gender and rules the north direction. It gives Kapha Dosha. It rules the foot and heels. <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=5:guru&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Guru</a> is the lord of Meena Rashi. <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=6:shukra&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Shukra</a> is exalted and <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=4:buddh&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Budh</a> is debilitated in Meena Rashi.&nbsp;</p>', 1, '', 0, 1, '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 0, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 899, '', '2014-02-01 12:46:18', 899, '2014-02-03 13:40:13', '*', '2014-02-01 12:46:18', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 33, 145, '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', 0, 3, 0, '', '', 12, '', 1),
