(228, 5, 1, '', '2014-02-03 13:18:19', 899, 4435, 'b6685bb07463705543037f2dd00ddd8cc5ff12bd', '{"id":5,"asset_id":"88","title":"Guru","alias":"guru","introtext":"<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; When an astrologer starts to read a horoscope the two things he is going to definitely check for is position of <a href=\\"index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=7:shani&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109\\">Saturn<\\/a> for bad results and Jupiter for good results. Jupiter is the most benefic planet in a horoscope. Popularly known as guru, it is considered a karaka for wealth, happines and well being. A well placed guru in a horoscope suggests a successful and happy life.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Jupiter is one planet which alone in a good position can liberate from all other negative influence of planets. It gives a positive outlook in life, gives a calm personality and pleasing appearance. A strong guru signifies a person who is learned, smart, calm and dignified. Guru gives a firm and unwavering faith in god and provides knowledge of Truth. Knowledge alone can free a soul from the worldy chains that plague the human soul and takes the soul closer to its maker aka The God.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Jupiter maybe the most benefic planet in a horoscope but it does have its share of negative influence like any other planet. People with Guru in a prominent position often are a bit chubby. Guru promotes well being but unfortunately it promotes laziness and gluttony also. Guru cause a person to be fat, chubby and easy going. When there is a crisis at work they maybe the calmest persons in the office but they will leave the proactive work to people with strong <a href=\\"index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=3:mangal&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109\\">Mangal<\\/a>. They are the ideal employers and marriage partners but not the most ideal employees. They rarely take up challenges which require them to sweat and they rarely have to drop a sweat to achieve something in life. Connection or Co-tenants like <a href=\\"index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=4:buddh&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109\\">Budha<\\/a> and <a href=\\"index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=6:shukra&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109\\">Shukra<\\/a> can cause all hell to break loose. Such people will go to any lenghts to make their pockets bigger and others people''s pockets smaller.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; All said and done, the benefits of Guru far outweigh its drawbacks. People with a strong guru are kind in nature and wonderful friends and family members. They easily get help from all spheres of life. People who crave for an easy lifestyle should definitely hope for a well placed Guru. Those less unfortunate souls who do not have a good disposition of Guru should make their way up the ladder through sheer hard work and dedication<\\/p>","fulltext":"","state":1,"catid":"10","created":"2014-02-01 11:46:31","created_by":"899","created_by_alias":"","modified":"2014-02-03 13:18:19","modified_by":"899","checked_out":"899","checked_out_time":"2014-02-03 13:18:11","publish_up":"2014-02-01 11:46:31","publish_down":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","images":"{\\"image_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"float_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_caption\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"float_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_caption\\":\\"\\"}","urls":"{\\"urla\\":false,\\"urlatext\\":\\"\\",\\"targeta\\":\\"\\",\\"urlb\\":false,\\"urlbtext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetb\\":\\"\\",\\"urlc\\":false,\\"urlctext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetc\\":\\"\\"}","attribs":"{\\"show_title\\":\\"\\",\\"link_titles\\":\\"\\",\\"show_tags\\":\\"\\",\\"show_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"info_block_position\\":\\"\\",\\"show_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_author\\":\\"\\",\\"link_author\\":\\"\\",\\"show_create_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_modify_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publish_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_item_navigation\\":\\"\\",\\"show_icons\\":\\"\\",\\"show_print_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_email_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_vote\\":\\"\\",\\"show_hits\\":\\"\\",\\"show_noauth\\":\\"\\",\\"urls_position\\":\\"\\",\\"alternative_readmore\\":\\"\\",\\"article_layout\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publishing_options\\":\\"\\",\\"show_article_options\\":\\"\\",\\"show_urls_images_backend\\":\\"\\",\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\":\\"\\"}","version":2,"ordering":"4","metakey":"","metadesc":"","access":"1","hits":"0","metadata":"{\\"robots\\":\\"\\",\\"author\\":\\"\\",\\"rights\\":\\"\\",\\"xreference\\":\\"\\"}","featured":"0","language":"*","xreference":""}', 0),
(229, 6, 1, '', '2014-02-03 13:18:52', 899, 6354, '5f4760e939d2b324fcd960d0cfb99ff8983086bd', '{"id":6,"asset_id":"90","title":"Shukra","alias":"shukra","introtext":"<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; When you think of romance and pleasures there is only one planet that can satisfy your quench for them. The name is Venus. Popularly known as Shukra in Vedic Astrology, shukra is the planet of pleasures, luxuries and music. It is identical to <a href=\\"index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=5:guru&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109\\">Guru<\\/a> as it gives abundant wealth but Shukra also gives pleasures and luxuries. While it does not have the humility to handle fame or wealth, it is guaranteed that a person with prominent Shukra would have lived his\\/her life to the fullest and given pleasure to all of his\\/her sensual organs.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Shukra is the kamdeva personified. All the romance in the world is a gift from Shukra. The beautiful women, melodious music and mesmerizing dance moves are all thanks to the great planet called Shukra. The life force or semen which brings another life on this earth is also governed by Shukra. All the sexual organs which provide pleasures are governed by Shukra. The delicacies like Chocolate and Pastries derive their sweetness from Shukra as Shukra is the karaka for Sweetness. The people with a great disposition of Shukra are attractive, wealthy, fashionable and charming. They are admirers of art, music, fashion and beauty.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; While Shukra is a karaka for everything beautiful and gorgeous it does have its downsides. Shukra promotes excessive sweetness and drug addiction. It does not know any limits to pleasures and romance. Most of the taboo activities are carried on when a person is either under the influence of Shukra or with association to Mangal and <a href=\\"index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=8:rahu&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109\\">Rahu<\\/a>. With <a href=\\"index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=3:mangal&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109\\">Mangal<\\/a> as a co-tenant or mutual aspect you could find a flirt and even a womaniser. All the marriages done on whims and instant attraction are due to Shukra-Mangal connections. When there is Rahu involved with Shukra marriage may even be with the wrong person and leads to bad reputation for the individual and their close relatives. Shukra causes drug, alcohol and sex addiction. Even addiction to medicines and prescribed drugs is possible with bad placement of Shukra.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Having said that it does do wonderful with <a href=\\"index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=2:chandra&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109\\">Chandra<\\/a> as co-tenant. The individual with Shukra+Chandra as co-tenant could have a romantic equation of epic proportions on par with Romeo-Juliet or Heer-Ranjhaana and remain inseparable throughout life. Shukra with Guru as co-tenant may give wealth, happiness and knowledge but many a times it is through illegal means. Shukra with Shani is quite bad as Shani''s negativity is a damp squid for sensual and pleasurable Shukra. But since both planets are friendly it rarely causes destruction. An aspect of Shani or Guru on Shukra is quite a blessing to have. Shukra also gives love for animals and provides benefits through them in a favourable placement.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Most beautiful woman and fortunate man have Shukra in a very good disposition. All the famous celebrities have a good Shukra or a favourable period of good Shukra. While Guru may give wealth, happiness and knowledge to a native leave it to Shukra to give you the finer things in life. Shukra natives are like a horse wihout a lease which can run off anywhere he\\/she pleases. The kind of ecstacy, pleasures and forbidden desires which Shukra provides can only be dreamt by other planets. Fame and fortune is abundant for people with a good Shukra.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Ofcourse with no boundary between acceptance and taboo most of the Shukra influenced people go bonkers after a certain time start resorting to drugs or even medicines to calm their mind. Romance and Sensual pleasures could be over the top but so is the risk of catching a venereal disease. Love takes a backseat and lust would control your mind and body unless there is a limiting aspect of Guru or Shani involved. The price of being a celebrityy is high with no privacy or peace but those who only crave for Page 3 lifestyle should start pleasing dear sweet aunty known as Shukra. For people with problematic Shukra praying to Lord Krishna or Goddess Laxmi for improving the condition and Goddess Santoshi Maa for decreasing the side-effects of afflicted Shukra is highly beneficial.<\\/p>","fulltext":"","state":1,"catid":"10","created":"2014-02-01 11:46:57","created_by":"899","created_by_alias":"","modified":"2014-02-03 13:18:52","modified_by":"899","checked_out":"899","checked_out_time":"2014-02-03 13:18:45","publish_up":"2014-02-01 11:46:57","publish_down":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","images":"{\\"image_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"float_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_caption\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"float_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_caption\\":\\"\\"}","urls":"{\\"urla\\":false,\\"urlatext\\":\\"\\",\\"targeta\\":\\"\\",\\"urlb\\":false,\\"urlbtext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetb\\":\\"\\",\\"urlc\\":false,\\"urlctext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetc\\":\\"\\"}","attribs":"{\\"show_title\\":\\"\\",\\"link_titles\\":\\"\\",\\"show_tags\\":\\"\\",\\"show_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"info_block_position\\":\\"\\",\\"show_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_author\\":\\"\\",\\"link_author\\":\\"\\",\\"show_create_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_modify_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publish_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_item_navigation\\":\\"\\",\\"show_icons\\":\\"\\",\\"show_print_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_email_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_vote\\":\\"\\",\\"show_hits\\":\\"\\",\\"show_noauth\\":\\"\\",\\"urls_position\\":\\"\\",\\"alternative_readmore\\":\\"\\",\\"article_layout\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publishing_options\\":\\"\\",\\"show_article_options\\":\\"\\",\\"show_urls_images_backend\\":\\"\\",\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\":\\"\\"}","version":2,"ordering":"3","metakey":"","metadesc":"","access":"1","hits":"0","metadata":"{\\"robots\\":\\"\\",\\"author\\":\\"\\",\\"rights\\":\\"\\",\\"xreference\\":\\"\\"}","featured":"0","language":"*","xreference":""}', 0),
(230, 7, 1, '', '2014-02-03 13:20:53', 899, 5624, '72d641c0ce32f41bce19e71239a3c7a76e5fdc8f', '{"id":7,"asset_id":"92","title":"Shani","alias":"shani","introtext":"&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; The word Shani seems to invoke fear in the hearts of people like no other planet. Shani represents scarcity, fear, oppression, old age and poverty. Well that alone seems to put this humble planet in the category of worst of the worst. By all means Shani can be said to be a malefic planet who brings adversities and havoc in our lives but the perspective has to change regarding how we look at adversities to understand the working of Shani a little more\\r\\n&nbsp; &nbsp; Let me start by saying that Shani is appointed as a judge by&nbsp;<a href=\\"http:\\/\\/www.sanatansociety.org\\/hindu_gods_and_goddesses\\/shiva.htm\\">Lord Shiva<\\/a> himself. A normal judiciary functions according to laws of the country and Shani functions according to divine laws of the nature. Shani is aware of most of our karmas and he provides punishments befitting our crimes. Most of the human beings are far from noble souls. We lie, steal, ridicule others and even deceive or backstab others. This is not limited to one birth time but continues over several births and rebirths. Though we may not be aware of these crimes, gramps Shani keeps a watchful eye over these karmas. Remember, he cannot punish you unless you have done some crime. &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;\\r\\n&nbsp; &nbsp;So why the fear of gramps Shani? Well, we are human beings after all. We cannot fathom why we need patience, hard work and discipline while the other guy gets the ferraris, the beautiful mansions and the iPhones. The sooner we learn the need for discipline, hard work, patience, fortitude and empathy the sooner does gramps Shani move out of our way. He does give wonderful results to those who plan the long road to success with honest and sincere efforts and plan betterment of the community and world. But those good fruits take a long, long time to come. By that time your patience is tested to the limits and your ego and arrogance is washed away. You are new and renewed all dignified, kind and considerate to your fellow beings.\\r\\n&nbsp; &nbsp;So is gramps Shani good or bad? Well he is bad cause we often plan shortcuts in life and easy way out of misery and suffering. That is the sole reason why Shani makes our lives a miserable hell. Say you are a prisoner in a jail and the warden catches you &nbsp;trying to sneak out of jail before your sentence is over. Most of us would assume that the warden would be very upset and may sentence us to more severe punishment. Same thing applies to Shani but he actually cares for his prisoners and wants them to be contributing members of the society. We do not like Shani cause he is a strict teacher who likes to whip now and then to teach some discipline and hard work to his students. No one likes to learn the things the hard way so to speak.\\r\\n&nbsp; Having said all this Shani has positive aspects in life also. Most of the guys who grow from rags to riches have Shani in an important disposition in their horoscope. Most of the people who make a difference in lives of others have Shani in exalted or own sign or in a good position. Shani destroys everything that is not sustainable over a long period of time. That includes relationships. Most of the divorces happen during the Saade-Saati or Shani Periods. Though it may seem like hell at that time after some time we come to realise that the relationship couldn''t have worked out and what happened was for the better. Our ego is destroyed and we learn the importance of patience and dignity. At the end of saade-saati most people develop a positive outlook towards lives.&nbsp;\\r\\n&nbsp; At the end of the day it all comes down to perspective. A simple, easy-going life is a choice of most but attainable by few. Those who believe in making lemonade, when lemons are provided fare much better in life then those who cry while looking at the lemons. Success is not defined by how high a person rises but how many times a person gets up after falling.&nbsp;\\r\\n","fulltext":"","state":1,"catid":"10","created":"2014-02-01 11:47:34","created_by":"899","created_by_alias":"","modified":"2014-02-03 13:20:53","modified_by":"899","checked_out":"899","checked_out_time":"2014-02-03 13:20:44","publish_up":"2014-02-01 11:47:34","publish_down":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","images":"{\\"image_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"float_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_caption\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"float_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_caption\\":\\"\\"}","urls":"{\\"urla\\":false,\\"urlatext\\":\\"\\",\\"targeta\\":\\"\\",\\"urlb\\":false,\\"urlbtext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetb\\":\\"\\",\\"urlc\\":false,\\"urlctext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetc\\":\\"\\"}","attribs":"{\\"show_title\\":\\"\\",\\"link_titles\\":\\"\\",\\"show_tags\\":\\"\\",\\"show_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"info_block_position\\":\\"\\",\\"show_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_author\\":\\"\\",\\"link_author\\":\\"\\",\\"show_create_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_modify_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publish_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_item_navigation\\":\\"\\",\\"show_icons\\":\\"\\",\\"show_print_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_email_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_vote\\":\\"\\",\\"show_hits\\":\\"\\",\\"show_noauth\\":\\"\\",\\"urls_position\\":\\"\\",\\"alternative_readmore\\":\\"\\",\\"article_layout\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publishing_options\\":\\"\\",\\"show_article_options\\":\\"\\",\\"show_urls_images_backend\\":\\"\\",\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\":\\"\\"}","version":2,"ordering":"2","metakey":"","metadesc":"","access":"1","hits":"0","metadata":"{\\"robots\\":\\"\\",\\"author\\":\\"\\",\\"rights\\":\\"\\",\\"xreference\\":\\"\\"}","featured":"0","language":"*","xreference":""}', 0),
(231, 8, 1, '', '2014-02-03 13:21:21', 899, 5823, 'bab78777fe2fb1d8246663eefc0f511f36eb6e89', '{"id":8,"asset_id":"94","title":"Rahu","alias":"rahu","introtext":"<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Rahu is a shadow planet and is considered the north node of the moon. It is also termed as a dragon''s head in some places while in vedic astrology Rahu has the head of a snake. According to vedic astrology, Rahu is responsible for causing eclipse to Sun and the Moon. Rahu is &nbsp;smokey and mysterious. He represents black arts, magic, taboo activities and foreigners. Rahu is an impersonator who tries to show the qualities he does not have. He is considered a malefic planet and astrologers make quite a fortune out of the so-called bad yogas associated with it. Well, the truth couldn''t be further off.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Rahu is a planet in vedic astrology and like in all planet''s case certain rules and regulations apply. The placement of Rahu at time of birth is fixed according to previous life karmas. Rahu is the most accurate measure to judge the sins of previous life karmas depending on his placement in horoscope along with its drishti. Rahu carries the mandate of putting a human being under illusion. Rahu encourages individuals to take risky and foolish decisions which only bring harm and loss for him. Ofcourse, sometimes it gives quite favorable results for people interested in forbidden desires and&nbsp;taboo activites. Not only that money, power, sex and fame are also abundant in a favorable period of Rahu.&nbsp;Most politicians have a very good Rahu. Rahu is a karaka for foreigners and everything mysterious. Rahu is one of the planets which in a favorable position can suggest a successful chance of going and settling abroad. Rahu in 4th house, 9th house and 12th house suggests if individual will live and stay away from home and in foreign locations.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Rahu magnifies the bad effects and lessens the good effects of planet which is its co-tenant. It is generally favorable if Rahu is alone in a house with no co-tenants and not casting drishti on any planet. Rahu causes eclipse to the Sun and the Moon. In other words the intelligence and rational thinking are hindered due to Rahu. Bad decisions, tough luck and mental problems follow. The individuals who have <a href=\\"index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=1:surya&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109\\">Surya<\\/a>+Rahu or <a href=\\"index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=2:chandra&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109\\">Chandra<\\/a>+Rahu in the same house are better off when they consult others for major decisions in their lives. Rahu+<a href=\\"index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=3:mangal&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109\\">Mangal<\\/a> is not as bad but cause relationships with siblings to go sour and also promotes anger, restlessness along with frustrations at not getting things done on time. Rahu+<a href=\\"index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=5:guru&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109\\">Guru<\\/a> is famously known as Viprachandal Yoga. The simple and wise Guru meets Rahu who is full of deceit and camaflouge. Naturally they don''t get along well. Rahu+Shukra is not as bad and actually gives quite good results. People with Shukra+Rahu are often driven by taboo activites and forbidden desires. The bad results of Rahu+Shukra are blind love followed by divorce. Rahu+<a href=\\"index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=7:shani&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109\\">Shani<\\/a> gives rise to Shapit yoga. It occurs after a long time and generally people born in these association have quite a hard life due to past life bad karmas.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Rahu is a strange planet to judge cause it is always trying to be pretentious. It tries to mirror <a href=\\"index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=6:shukra&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109\\">Shukra<\\/a>&nbsp;but he is an imposter. Though in the present age it is quite good to have Rahu in an influental house. Today the world judges book by its cover and people who are engaged in showboating, impersonating and hypocricy enjoy quite good status. All aspiring politicians must hope and pray for a better Rahu.&nbsp;<\\/p>","fulltext":"","state":1,"catid":"10","created":"2014-02-01 11:48:00","created_by":"899","created_by_alias":"","modified":"2014-02-03 13:21:21","modified_by":"899","checked_out":"899","checked_out_time":"2014-02-03 13:21:14","publish_up":"2014-02-01 11:48:00","publish_down":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","images":"{\\"image_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"float_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_caption\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"float_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_caption\\":\\"\\"}","urls":"{\\"urla\\":false,\\"urlatext\\":\\"\\",\\"targeta\\":\\"\\",\\"urlb\\":false,\\"urlbtext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetb\\":\\"\\",\\"urlc\\":false,\\"urlctext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetc\\":\\"\\"}","attribs":"{\\"show_title\\":\\"\\",\\"link_titles\\":\\"\\",\\"show_tags\\":\\"\\",\\"show_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"info_block_position\\":\\"\\",\\"show_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_author\\":\\"\\",\\"link_author\\":\\"\\",\\"show_create_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_modify_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publish_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_item_navigation\\":\\"\\",\\"show_icons\\":\\"\\",\\"show_print_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_email_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_vote\\":\\"\\",\\"show_hits\\":\\"\\",\\"show_noauth\\":\\"\\",\\"urls_position\\":\\"\\",\\"alternative_readmore\\":\\"\\",\\"article_layout\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publishing_options\\":\\"\\",\\"show_article_options\\":\\"\\",\\"show_urls_images_backend\\":\\"\\",\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\":\\"\\"}","version":2,"ordering":"1","metakey":"","metadesc":"","access":"1","hits":"0","meta